reviewText: Anybody But Hyacinth is wounderful.  No matter which Hyacinth movie you buy you can't go wrong. I love all of the videos of "Keeping Up Appearances."  I have all of the releases that are out.  And watch it  on PBS every week.  I wish they would release the older shows even on TV.  I am truly addicted to Hyacinth "Buckets" AH "Bouquet.
